<a name="nyw"><h1><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2"> Marine vessels serving New York City </kw></h1></a>
    <p></p>
    <p>
    <span class="Ital"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">by Walter Goyzueta, John Chen, Kevin Byrnes, and Rudy Ferro</kw></span>
    </p>
    <p>
    </p><div class="Contents"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">
Quick reference</kw><br>
<a href="#nyw45"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">— History</kw></a><br>
<a href="#nyw46"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">— Vessels and volume</kw></a><br>
<a href="#nyw47"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">— Operation</kw></a><br>
<a href="312011.html" onclick="javascript:textWin('312011.html',450,350);return false;"><span class="Bold&quot;"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Web extra:</kw></span><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1"> Summary of New York's water pollution control plants</kw></a><br>
<a href="#nyw48"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">— Water quality survey of New York Harbor</kw></a><br>
<a href="312012.html" onclick="javascript:textWin('312012.html',450,350);return false;"><span class="Bold&quot;"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Web extra:</kw></span><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1"> Areas of New York's CSO Abatement Program</kw></a><br>
